					<p align="justify">Model 2: Business to Government. Another potential business model we are exploring is based on engaging in a contract with the United States government or government entities. By helping to avert major public health crises and preparing adequately for future outbreaks, our technology could help groups like the CDC and NIH predict the severity of future crises.</p>
